Decompose the problem into a small number of functional subproblems that represent the necessary algorithmic stages to solve the task (e.g., parsing, modeling, optimization, or verification). Ensure the number of helpers is kept to a minimum to avoid exceeding orchestration limits.

Return exactly one JSON object in this format:
{
  "schema_name": "eywa_node_response",
  "schema_version": "v1",
  "orchestration_decision": "delegate",
  "decision_notes": "optional string",
  "helpers": [
    {
      "label": "helper_1",
      "instructions": "plain-text subproblem for the first helper"
    }
  ],
  "synthesis_brief": "how the parent should combine the child results"
}
